    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Straps with looped ends that are components of bridles attached to the headpiece. These are mounted on a horse's forehead between eyes and ears so that the bridle remains secure. Brow bands may also be decorative.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
